usually takes months, not weeks, to go from a base to a blow-off top. If you force this acceleration with leverage, one small \"shakeout\" (dump) wipes you out.\n\n### My Honest Advice:\nSince your brother is involved, you have to look out for him. Betting the house on a \"Phase Transition\" in 5 weeks is gambling, not investing.\n\n**The smarter play:**\nSince you are confident in the model, use the $150k to buy **seats** in the parabola, not to speed it up.\n\n1.  Keep the house.\n2.  Buy the max amount of BTC you can afford **without a HELOC**.\n3.  Show your brother the chart.\n\nIf you can't comfortably lose the $150k (even if BTC goes to $0), you shouldn't be using leverage. The \"math\" only works if you survive to collect. If you lose the house, the Fibonacci spiral matters zero.",
